org.efaps.admin.datamodel

Class Type

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.efaps.admin.AbstractAdminObject
      • org.efaps.admin.datamodel.AbstractDataModelObject
        • org.efaps.admin.datamodel.Type
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, CacheObjectInterface
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AttributeSet, Classification

    public class Type
extends AbstractDataModelObject
    This is the class for the type description. The type description holds information about creation of a new instance of a type with default values.
    Version:
    $Id$
    Author:
    The eFaps Team
